    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Haunt Hunter</i> blends psychological horror, exploration, and survival mechanics set inside the eerie halls of <strong>Anya Manon Hospital</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Explore &amp; Investigate -</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Search dark rooms, labs, and wards for notes to uncover what happened within the hospital.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252220/extras/0c4b744714cff5fa27fc980b651d95a3.poster.avif?t=1761400313\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252220/extras/0c4b744714cff5fa27fc980b651d95a3.webm?t=1761400313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252220/extras/0c4b744714cff5fa27fc980b651d95a3.mp4?t=1761400313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Combat System -</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Defend yourself with the limited weapons found across the hospital. Ammunition and resources are scarce, so every shot counts. Use your Melee Combat moves to defend yourself in some situations.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Immersive Horror -</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic lighting, haunting design, and enemy encounters create a tense, ever-changing experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252220/extras/9615b57b21d0cee224f9d44d822404fa.poster.avif?t=1761400313\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252220/extras/9615b57b21d0cee224f9d44d822404fa.webm?t=1761400313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252220/extras/9615b57b21d0cee224f9d44d822404fa.mp4?t=1761400313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
